@startuml object_risk_to_warning_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Object Risk To Warning Signal Flow\n(FRADAR / FCA -> ADAS -> CGW -> IVI / CLU)

participant "FRADAR\nobject track source" as FRADAR #E8F7E8
participant "FCA\nFCW / AEB request view" as FCA #FFF4CC
participant "ADAS\nobject-risk owner" as ADAS #FCE8FF
participant "CGW\neffective warning gate" as CGW #FFF4CC
participant "IVI\nwarning render / popup" as IVI #E8F0FE
participant "CLU\ncluster warning output" as CLU #E8F0FE

== Object Perception ==

activate FRADAR
FRADAR -> ADAS : object track / range / relSpeed / confidence
note right of FRADAR
Representative perception inputs
- objectTrackValid
- objectRange
- objectRelSpeed
- objectConfidence
end note
deactivate FRADAR

activate FCA
ADAS -> FCA : decelAssistReq / objectRiskClass / TTC basis
FCA -> ADAS : FCW/AEB context contribution
note right of FCA
Representative outcomes
- fcwState
- aebRequest
end note
deactivate FCA

== ADAS Object-Risk Decision ==

activate ADAS
FRADAR -> ADAS : perception inputs
ADAS -> ADAS : calcObjectRisk()
ADAS -> ADAS : calcObjectRiskClass()
ADAS -> ADAS : objectEventCode = 1381 / 1382 / 1383
ADAS -> ADAS : selectedAlertDecisionLevel / Type
ADAS -> CGW : CoreState::selectedAlertDecisionLevel
ADAS -> CGW : CoreState::selectedAlertDecisionType
ADAS -> CGW : Core::objectRiskClass / objectEventCode
ADAS -> CGW : frmAdasChassisStatusMsg
note right of ADAS
Representative seams
- Core::objectRiskClass
- Core::objectEventCode
- CoreState::selectedAlertDecisionLevel
- CoreState::selectedAlertDecisionType
end note
deactivate ADAS

== CGW Effective Gate ==

activate CGW
ADAS -> CGW : decision seams + object event
CGW -> CGW : timeout / boundary / fail-safe adjustment
CGW -> CGW : selectedAlertEffectiveLevel / Type
CGW -> IVI : effective alert seams
CGW -> CLU : effective alert seams
note right of CGW
Gateway side effects
- selectedAlertGateReason
- object safety visibility
- fail-safe escalation
end note
deactivate CGW

== Warning Rendering ==

activate IVI
CGW -> IVI : effective alert level/type
IVI -> IVI : deriveWarningTextCode()
IVI -> CLU : frmClusterWarningMsg
IVI -> CLU : frmClusterNotifMsg
note right of IVI
Representative outputs
- Cluster::warningTextCode
- popup / notif state
- warningBeepState
end note
deactivate IVI

activate CLU
IVI -> CLU : warning / notif
CLU -> CLU : update cluster warning text
deactivate CLU

note over FRADAR, CLU
Representative runtime chain
1. FRADAR and FCA provide object-risk context
2. ADAS computes object risk class and decision alert
3. CGW gates decision into effective warning
4. IVI and CLU render text / notification to the driver
end note

@enduml
